Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}为将你守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:52.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我甘愿奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:58.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:13.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}苍焰是为使两人邂逅的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:17.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将频频闪现的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:22.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}照耀得鲜明活现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:26.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}纵有天负伤倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:31.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也终要在我怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:36.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}安详地沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:41.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}紧拥着坚定信念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:46.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}追随之心将不受时空的阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:52.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只愿你放出慑人光芒的手心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:59.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}会映有我的身影
